This code is based on the Anisotropic Diffusion filter proposed by Perona and Malik, as proposed in Pietro Perona and Jitendra Malik, "Scale-space and edge detection using anisotropic diffusion", IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence, vol. 12, no. 4, pp. 629-639 (July 1990).
